<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 1 (Caius) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rubia</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ねぇ、カイウス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, Caius.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's up?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウスは
過去を変えたいって思った事ないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Have you ever wanted to change the past?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あるよ。　何度もある</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have. Plenty of times.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だけどそんな事出来ないさ。
たしかに今まで辛い事もいっぱいあったけど
オレには大切な思い出だってある</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I can't do something like that. It's true I've
been through a lot of hard times up through
now, but I have a bunch of precious memories.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そういう思い出が詰まった
“今”を否定する事なんて、オレには出来ない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't just deny "right now" to myself,
when it's full of memories like that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だから変えちゃいけない。
受け入れなきゃいけないんだ。
どんな運命でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why we can't change it.
We have to accept it.
No matter what our fate is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それはわかってるんだ。　だけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I do know that. But...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やっぱりこんなのむかつくんだ！
どうして獣人なんてものを作った！？
気に入らない！　腹が立つ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>In the end, it's still so aggravating! Why did I
have to be a beastman?! I hate it! It's infuriating!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だからオレは
一発ぶん殴ってやりたいんだ！
運命を作った神って奴を！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's why I wanna get a punch in on him!
The guy who made fate a thing!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ホント……バカね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You really... are dumb, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
